description: 4BD/2BA house near Alma Schrader elementary school.  Home includes a finished basement with two bedrooms, a bathroom, and a laundry room, one car attached garage, and fenced in yard back yard.  Appliances include refrigerator, microwave, dish washer, and electric stove.  Central A/C, gas heat, and gas water heater. Small pet, under 20 pound, accepted with additional fees.   In the Alma Schrader district. Minimum Deposit $1,200.00.
